        <manvolnum>3G</manvolnum>
    </refmeta>
    <refnamediv>
        <refname>groupMemoryBarrier</refname>
        <refpurpose>controls the ordering of memory transaction issued shader invocation relative to a work group</refpurpose>
    </refnamediv>
    <refsynopsisdiv><title>Declaration</title>
        <funcsynopsis>
            <funcprototype>
                <funcdef>void <function>groupMemoryBarrier</function></funcdef>
                <paramdef>void</paramdef>
            </funcprototype>
        </funcsynopsis>
    </refsynopsisdiv>
    <refsect1 id="description"><title>Description</title>
        <para>
            <function>groupMemoryBarrier</function> waits on the completion of all memory accesses performed
            by an invocation of a compute shader relative to the same access performed by other invocations
            in the same work group and then returns with no other effect.
        </para>
    </refsect1>
